channel.title: Its All About Defang :: SANS Holiday Hack Challenge 2025
channel.description: Objective Difficulty: 1/5 Find Ed Skoudis upstairs in City Hall and help him troubleshoot a clever phishing tool in his cozy office. Ed Skoudis mission statement I’m the Founder of Counter Hack Innovations, the team that brings you the SANS Holiday Hack Challenge for the last 22 years. I’m also the President of the SANS Technology Institute College, which has over 2,300 students studying for their Bachelor’s Degrees, Master’s Degrees, and various certificates.
